headline: Dominion Energy and the Library of Virginia Honor Four Leaders as "Strong Men & Women in Virginia History"
summary: RICHMOND, Va., February 12, 2026--Dominion Energy and the Library of Virginia are pleased to announce the 2026 Strong Men & Women in Virginia History honorees and Student Creative Expressions Contest finalists.
